Description

Latest Rajasthan Government Jobs for graduates have been published by Rajasthan Rajya Vidyut Utpadan Nigam Limited for  Assistant Personnel Officer, Junior Legal Officer, Junior Accountant, Stenographer & Junior Assistant/Commercial Assistant-II vacancies in Rajasthan. If you are searching for a government job in Rajasthan then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for these vacancies, from 07-06-2021, and till the last date. If you are interested in all these vacancies in Rajasthan and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.

Application fee

  • Mode of application is Online
  • For UR (Gen)/EWS if the annual income of family is Rs.2.50 lakh/ more: 1200/-
  • For UR (Gen)/EWS if annual income of of family is less than Rs.2.50 lakh/ SC/ ST/ BC/ MBC/ PWD (PH): 1000/-

Important dates

  •  The starting date to apply in these posts is 07-06-2021.
  •  Last date to apply in these posts is 21-06-2021 

Age Limit Criteria

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 18 to 40  years old. 

Detailed vacancies:

RVUNL Pay Scale

  • According to the information given by the Rajasthan Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is as per norms.

How to apply for RVUNL Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the Assistant Personnel Officer, Junior Legal Officer, Junior Accountant, Stenographer & Junior Assistant/Commercial Assistant-II. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of RVUNL and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by RVUNL.
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.
